{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"14b81de0-2a27-480c-971f-43420f129d9b","content":"Now I have a clear picture. Here's what needs to change for xUnit v3:\n\n1. **`.csproj`**: Replace packages with `xunit.v3`, add `<OutputType>Exe</OutputType>`, remove `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` and `xunit.runner.visualstudio`\n2. **`global.json`**: Switch test runner to `Microsoft.Testing.Platform`\n3. **`CalculatorTests.cs`**: No code changes needed — `[Fact]`, `[Theory]`, `[InlineData]`, and `Assert` keep the same API","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_014JDRJSTSu1AQipSg2oSmd3","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-9ebb22e48c924963978d22fa009cc56e/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>\n    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>\n    <IsPackable>false</IsPackable>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk\" Version=\"18.3.0\" />\n    <PackageReference Include=\"xunit\" Version=\"2.9.3\" />\n    <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.runner.visualstudio\" Version=\"2.8.2\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>","new_str":"<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>\n    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>\n    <IsPackable>false</IsPackable>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.v3\" Version=\"1.1.0\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-9ebb22e48c924963978d22fa009cc56e/TestProject.csproj."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_013KSNxiY715LgogcRSYkYem","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-9ebb22e48c924963978d22fa009cc56e/global.json","old_str":"{\n  \"test\": {\n    \"runner\": \"VSTest\"\n  }\n}","new_str":"{\n  \"test\": {\n    \"runner\": \"Microsoft.Testing.Platform\"\n  }\n}"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-9ebb22e48c924963978d22fa009cc56e/global.json."}],"interactionId":"01dd9bea-a227-4bcb-b169-4848d349c639","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Now I understand the current state. Let me plan the migration from xUnit.net v2 to v3:\n\n1. **Project file changes:**\n   - Replace `xunit` (v2) with `xunit.v3` (v3)\n   - Remove `xunit.runner.visualstudio` (not needed in v3; the runner is built-in)\n   - Remove `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` (not needed in v3)\n   - Change output type to `Exe` (v3 test projects are executables)\n   - Remove `IsPackable` if desired (or keep it)\n\n\n2. **global.json changes:**\n   - Update the test runner configuration to use `Microsoft.Testing.Platform` instead of `VSTest`, since xUnit v3 projects are self-contained executables that use this platform by default.\n3. **Code changes:**\n   - The namespace remains `Xunit` for basic attributes, so most test code should work without modification.\n   - Test methods continue to return `void` or `Task` as before.\n\nFor the migration itself, I need to swap the `xunit` package for `xunit.v3`, remove the `xunit.runner.visualstudio` and `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` dependencies, and configure the test project as an executable with `<OutputType>Exe</OutputType>`. Then I'll update global.json to point to the Microsoft.Testing.Platform runner.\n\nMaking these changes now...","outputTokens":1224,"requestId":"9820:3C606F:27CFBD:346C43:69FFE3FB"},"id":"2eb3c751-d508-4718-b10b-59879280d198","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:49:01.669Z","parentId":"119a6edc-bf04-42c7-b831-ed22f07836e0"}
